{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "prom-vs-ch-nfr",
  "title": "Prometheus vs ClickHouse — Сравнение NFR",
  "description": "Сравнение нефункциональных требований: Prometheus (TSDB) vs ClickHouse (MergeTree). Все метрики поступают через Prometheus datasource — Prometheus scrapes себя и ClickHouse /metrics endpoint.",
  "tags": ["comparison", "prometheus", "clickhouse", "nfr"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Prometheus vs ClickHouse: Нефункциональные требования\n\nОба хранилища получают **одинаковый поток метрик** через OTel Collector. Сравниваем по: потреблению памяти, CPU, скорости записи, объёму хранилища, кардинальности и задержке запросов.\n\n> **Prometheus** — time-series база с PromQL. **ClickHouse** — колоночная база с SQL. Один источник данных, два разных движка."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Потребление памяти (Memory)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "RAM — Prometheus vs ClickHouse",
      "description": "RSS память процессов. Prometheus: process_resident_memory_bytes. ClickHouse: ClickHouseAsyncMetrics_MemoryResident (реальная RSS) + ClickHouseMetrics_MemoryTracking (трекинг внутри CH).",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 8,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 500000000 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 1000000000 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Prometheus RSS" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#E05F27", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "ClickHouse RSS" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#1F78C1", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "ClickHouse Memory Tracking" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#5794F2", "mode": "fixed" } },
              { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "fill": "dash", "dash": [4, 4] } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"] }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "process_resident_memory_bytes{job=\"prometheus\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Prometheus RSS",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "ClickHouseAsyncMetrics_MemoryResident{job=\"clickhouse\"}",
          "legendFormat": "ClickHouse RSS",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "ClickHouseMetrics_MemoryTracking{job=\"clickhouse\"}",
          "legendFormat": "ClickHouse Memory Tracking",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Текущий RAM — Prometheus",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 300000000 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 700000000 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "orientation": "auto", "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "process_resident_memory_bytes{job=\"prometheus\"}",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Текущий RAM — ClickHouse",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 12 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 300000000 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 700000000 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "orientation": "auto", "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "ClickHouseAsyncMetrics_MemoryResident{job=\"clickhouse\"}",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Разница RAM (CH / Prom)",
      "description": "Коэффициент потребления памяти: ClickHouse / Prometheus. < 1 — ClickHouse экономнее.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 12 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "none",
          "decimals": 2,
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 2 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "orientation": "auto", "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "ClickHouseAsyncMetrics_MemoryResident{job=\"clickhouse\"} / process_resident_memory_bytes{job=\"prometheus\"}",
          "legendFormat": "CH/Prom ratio",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Пик RAM за 1ч — оба",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 12 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "bytes", "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" } }
      },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["max"] }, "orientation": "horizontal", "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "process_resident_memory_bytes{job=\"prometheus\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Prometheus",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "ClickHouseAsyncMetrics_MemoryResident{job=\"clickhouse\"}",
          "legendFormat": "ClickHouse",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Нагрузка CPU",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
